14 triangulations at n=8 and for all 5 violating triangulations at n=10, the
planar dual was built face-by-face from the rotation system, its faces traced,
and each dual face shown to surround a unique primal vertex with
face size == primal degree.  Result: ALL 19 LINES VERIFIED (PASS).

